Insider Activity


Individual




Helen E. Dragas



Ms. Helen E. Dragas is Independent Director at Dominion Resources, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer at The Dragas Cos. She is on the Board of Directors at Dominion Resources, Inc.
Ms. Dragas also served on the board at Commonwealth Transportation Board and State Council of Higher Education for Virginia.
She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Virginia and an MBA from the University of Virginia.



