THE DRAGAS PROMISE
We promise:
A well-built home constructed with quality materials by seasoned contractors who know and meet our rigid standards.
A well-designed home that makes maximum use of every square foot so you get the most for your investment.
A well-planned community– a true neighborhood, attractively designed and landscaped, and professionally maintained to protect and enhance your investment for years to come.
A reasonable price that is more than competitive, because we are able to offer more for your home-buying dollar, including many amenities and features that other builders may consider upgrades.
Responsive service to our homebuyers– even long after the sale- thanks to the attention to detail our exceptional customer care group provides to you and your neighbors.


 





































